	<div class="title">The Introduction</div>
	<div class="container">
		<p class="style1">So in case you were wondering what this is all about...</p>
		<p class="style2">
			Nift is a high-performance cross-platform unopinionated framework for building the web.
		</p>
		<p class="style3">It's <strong>lightning fast</strong> (<a href="https://hugo-vs-nift.gitlab.io/" style="color: white !important">evidence</a>), open source (<a href="https://choosealicense.com/licenses/mit/" style="color: white !important">MIT license</a>) and developed from the ground up in <strong>C++</strong>. Use it for any of your personal or commercial projects!</p>
	</div>
</section>

